er service scale, compliance review, knowledge fragmentation, manual back-office processes, product/policy search. Insurance challenges: claims operations, policy search, risk assessment, document-heavy workflows, customer response time. Use agents such as Compliance Assistant, Customer Intelligence Agent, Risk Review Agent, Knowledge Search Agent, Executive Dashboard Agent, Banking Knowledge Agent, Relationship Manager Copilot, Contract Intelligence Agent, Claims Triage Agent, Policy Intelligence Agent, Underwriting Copilot. No fake clients, fake logos, fake ROI, or guarantees. Use clean graphics, carousels/tabs, Framer Motion if available, and responsive mobile layouts. Run lint/build.\"\n153 |   },\n154 |   {\n155 |     \"id\": \"19-industries-batch2-health-education\",\n156 |     \"title\": \"Design Healthcare Life Sciences Education pages\",\n157 |     \"scope\": \"page-family-design\",\n158 |     \"target\": \"Industries batch 2\",\n159 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n160 |     \"prompt\": \"Upgrade /industries/healthcare, /industries/life-sciences, and /industries/education using the same premium industry family design but tailored visuals and content. Do not touch landing page. Healthcare challenges: operational complexity, patient communication workflows, staff knowledge access, administrative burden, compliance-sensitive processes. Life Sciences challenges: research documentation, regulatory workflows, knowledge management, trial operations support, cross-functional collaboration. Education challenges: student support, faculty enablement, knowledge access, university operations, AI labs and learning platforms. Suggested agents: Care Operations Copilot, Knowledge Search Agent, Document Intelligence Agent, Scheduling Assistant, Executive Dashboard Agent, Research Knowledge Agent, Regulatory Document Assistant, Trial Operations Copilot, Student Support Agent, Faculty Assistant, Learning Assistant, University Operations Copilot. Do not make medical diagnosis claims. Do not make compliance guarantees. Include challenge landscape, reference solution, architecture visual, agent map, outcome levers, demo preview, Talk to Agent CTA, related platforms such as University OneVerse and AI Academy where relevant. Add page-specific graphics, tabs/carousels, subtle motion, and excellent mobile layout. Run lint/build.\"\n161 |   },\n162 |   {\n163 |     \"id\": \"20-industries-batch3-ops-retail-mining\",\n164 |     \"title\": \"Design Manufacturing Retail Mining pages\",\n165 |     \"scope\": \"page-family-design\",\n166 |     \"target\": \"Industries batch 3\",\n167 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n168 |     \"prompt\": \"Upgrade /industries/manufacturing, /industries/retail, and /industries/mining using the premium industry solution family. Do not touch landing page. Manufacturing challenges: production visibility, maintenance workflows, quality management, supplier coordination, operational knowledge transfer. Retail challenges: customer experience, merchandising operations, store support, inventory visibility, employee knowledge access. Mining challenges: field operations, safety workflows, asset visibility, remote site knowledge access, operational reporting. Suggested agents: Maintenance Copilot, Quality Intelligence Agent, Procurement Copilot, Field Operations Agent, Executive Dashboard Agent, Customer Experience Agent, Store Operations Copilot, Merchandising Intelligence Agent, Safety Knowledge Agent. Related platforms: RetailMesh for Retail, OREMesh for Mining, Factory/Control Center for Manufacturing. Include challenge maps, reference solution, architecture, agent map, outcome levers, demo preview, CTA. No fake clients, fake logos, fake ROI numbers. Premium 2026 UI with carousels/tabs/graphics/motion. Run lint/build.\"\n169 |   },\n170 |   {\n171 |     \"id\": \"21-industries-batch4-regulated-public-telecom\",\n172 |     \"title\": \"Design Energy Telecom Government Public Sector pages\",\n173 |     \"scope\": 